---
title: Grilled Asparagus and Duck Summer Salad with Balsamic Blueberry Vinaigrette, Walnuts and Goat Cheese
description: In this summer-ready recipe, flame-kissed asparagus spears deliver some smoky goodness, while a balsamic-blueberry vinaigrette drizzled over toasted walnuts, plums and succulent duck breasts brings the plate alive.
